<anchor id="hash_8h_1hash"/> <simplesect kind="par"><title>Detailed Description </title><para>SHA1 checksum calculation uses the <ulink url="https://github.com/Mbed-TLS/mbedtls">mbedtls crypto library</ulink>. For a detailed documentation see <ulink url="https://mbed-tls.readthedocs.io/en/latest/kb/how-to/mbedtls-tutorial/">Mbed TLS tutorial</ulink>. <linebreak/>
